resources.string: Results file ready. Tap to open.
Please select a prompts file first.

This application relies on AICore Beta, so let\'s install it first:\n \n 1. Join the aicore-experimental Google group\n \n 2. Opt in to the Android AICore testing program\n \n 3. Go for a walk. An hour later, in the Google Play store app, make sure you have \"Android AICore (Beta)\" installed. If the \"(Beta)\" suffix is not present, update your apps, reboot, and wait it a bit more.\n \n If you still get this screen, please file an issue on the project\'s GitHub issue tracker, ideally with an ADB logcat dump.\n \n Thank you for your patience!
